catalina.sh in the stand-alone has this:

{code}
Only set CATALINA_HOME if not already set
[ -z "$CATALINA_HOME" ] && CATALINA_HOME=`cd "$PRGDIR/.." >/dev/null; pwd` 
on lines 113 and 114
{code}

